&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen to join the Informatics Project Management Team as a Project Manager. The post holder will manage a number of IT projects to support the wider Trust and will ensure that work is appropriately scoped, planned and delivered.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’re looking for someone with enthusiasm, keen to develop their skills and to play an important part in supporting the delivery of the Trust’s objectives. Working in a fast-paced environment you will need to have the ability to plan, multi-task and ensure that your project teams deliver to their agreed timescales. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Name: Ged Hussey&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Job title: Implementation Programme Manager&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Email address: gerrard.hussey@nhs.net&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Telephone number: 0151 678 5111 Ext: 8489&lt;/p&gt;
